# Data Contract Builder (Zeenea DCB)

SPA React prototype for creating and managing data contracts aligned with **ODCS v3.1.0**.

Current prototype characteristics:

- Frontend-only React application.
- Persistence through `localStorage` (`data-contracts-v1`).
- Simulated publication / version history; no external repository sync is connected.
- No backend, no real authentication, no real Zeenea API.
- UI Kit source-of-truth rules are defined separately in `.cursor/rules/ui-kit-source-of-truth.mdc`.
- React/UI implementation conventions are defined separately in `.cursor/rules/react-ui.mdc`.

## Stack

- React 19 + TypeScript strict + Vite 8.
- Tailwind CSS 4.
- Actian theme tokens in `src/index.css`.
- UI primitives in `src/components/ui/`.
- Product/shared patterns in `src/components/shared/`.
- Alias `@/` → `src/`.

